org.transitime.ipc.data

Class IpcVehicleComplete

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.transitime.ipc.data.IpcVehicle
      • org.transitime.ipc.data.IpcVehicleGtfsRealtime
        • org.transitime.ipc.data.IpcVehicleComplete
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class IpcVehicleComplete
extends IpcVehicleGtfsRealtime
    Extension of IpcVehicle class so that all info describing vehicle is included. All this info is put into the VehicleDataCache so that can get whatever data is needed be the remote clients. In particular, includes additional info for SIRI feed. Made a separate class from IpcVehicle since the SIRI feed is not expected to get significant use (it is a poor interface) and don't want to bog down all the other IpcVehicle requests with extraneous data.
    Author:
    SkiBu Smith
